rows.name:
Ask Alex about his thoughts on
the xenoforms living in NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Alex if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0001
rows.name:
I finally return from a long deployment and find
New LA's been turned into a zoo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0002
rows.name:
All these freaks strut around like they own the city!
What the hell is the provisional government thinking?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Wait. Chausson granted them RESIDENCY?!
Unbelievable. Absolutely unbelievable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0008
rows.name:
Has everyone forgotten that it was xenos who
destroyed our freaking home?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0009
rows.name:
And after a long and grueling journey, who forced us
to crash-land on this godforsaken planet? I'll tell you!
More xenos![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010201_MSG0010
rows.name:
This city was supposed to be built for us humans.
But I can say that till I'm blue in the faceâ€”it's clear
that no one's gonna do a damn thing about it.[ST:wait ]
